<font color="japanese">ウオオオオ！

200
00:12:45,014 --> 00:12:47,767
<font color="japanese">お前の憎しみと悲しみを…

201
00:12:48,392 --> 00:12:50,311
<font color="japanese">私では無理なのか？

202
00:12:51,061 --> 00:12:51,687
<font color="japanese">健夫！

203
00:12:51,771 --> 00:12:53,689
<font color="japanese">ウウウウ…

204
00:12:54,815 --> 00:12:55,691
<font color="japanese">もう⸺

205
00:12:56,192 --> 00:12:58,944
<font color="japanese">健夫の精神を
<font color="japanese">シャットダウンするしか⸺

206
00:12:59,570 --> 00:13:00,696
<font color="japanese">ない！

207
00:13:09,288 --> 00:13:11,707
<font color="japanese">グアアアア…

208
00:13:14,627 --> 00:13:17,922
<font color="japanese">チャールズが 健夫の精神を
<font color="japanese">シャットダウンして

209
00:13:18,005 --> 00:13:20,216
<font color="japanese">すべてを終わらせようと
<font color="japanese">しているわ！

210
00:13:20,841 --> 00:13:22,009
<font color="japanese">そんな…！

211
00:13:22,635 --> 00:13:23,636
<font color="japanese">チャールズも⸺

212
00:13:24,136 --> 00:13:28,265
<font color="japanese">健夫の精神の中で
<font color="japanese">一緒に消えるつもりよ

213
00:13:28,349 --> 00:13:29,058
<font color="japanese">何だと？

214
00:13:29,141 --> 00:13:30,518
<font color="japanese">チャールズ！

215
00:13:31,644 --> 00:13:33,729
<font color="japanese">なんてバカなことしやがる！

216
00:13:34,355 --> 00:13:35,940
<font color="japanese">佐々木先生！

217
00:13:36,023 --> 00:13:38,484
<font color="japanese">ウウウ… ウウウ…

218
00:13:38,984 --> 00:13:39,944
<font color="japanese">健夫！

219
00:13:40,569 --> 00:13:42,446
<font color="japanese">連れていくなら私を…

220
00:13:43,447 --> 00:13:45,950
<font color="japanese">お母さんを
<font color="japanese">連れていきなさい！

221
00:13:46,033 --> 00:13:49,662
<font color="japanese">グオオオオ…

222
00:13:50,996 --> 00:13:53,415
<font color="japanese">お前一人だけ<font color="japanese">行(ゆ)<font color="japanese">かせはしない

223
00:13:54,208 --> 00:13:57,795
<font color="japanese">その苦しみも
<font color="japanese">私がともに背負う

224
00:13:57,878 --> 00:13:58,587
<font color="japanese">ダメよ！

225
00:13:58,671 --> 00:13:59,171
<font color="japanese">んっ？

226
00:14:00,548 --> 00:14:01,924
<font color="japanese">こんなの…

227
00:14:02,007 --> 00:14:04,176
<font color="japanese">こんなの絶対ダメ！

228
00:14:05,135 --> 00:14:06,762
<font color="japanese">はっ　久子…

229
00:14:07,763 --> 00:14:09,390
<font color="japanese">こんな形で⸺

230
00:14:10,140 --> 00:14:11,183
<font color="japanese">終わらせない！

231
00:14:30,035 --> 00:14:31,161
<font color="japanese">健夫

232
00:14:31,662 --> 00:14:32,788
<font color="japanese">久子だよ

233
00:14:33,706 --> 00:14:36,584
<font color="japanese">覚えてるでしょ？
<font color="japanese">このヤケド

234
00:14:36,667 --> 00:14:38,294
<font color="japanese">ウウウウ…

235
00:14:38,878 --> 00:14:39,795
<font color="japanese">うん

236
00:14:39,879 --> 00:14:41,755
<font color="japanese">つらい思い出だよね

237
00:14:42,631 --> 00:14:43,299
<font color="japanese">でも⸺

238
00:14:44,508 --> 00:14:47,052
<font color="japanese">素敵な思い出だって
<font color="japanese">あるじゃない

239
00:14:47,595 --> 00:14:48,596
<font color="japanese">たくさん

240
00:14:49,388 --> 00:14:50,306
<font color="japanese">たくさん

241
00:14:50,890 --> 00:14:51,599
<font color="japanese">うっ

242
00:14:52,141 --> 00:14:53,309
<font color="japanese">たくさん！

243
00:14:54,101 --> 00:14:57,313
<font color="japanese">グウ… ウオオオオオ

244
00:14:57,396 --> 00:14:58,188
<font color="japanese">クッ！

245
00:14:58,272 --> 00:14:59,023
<font color="japanese">あっ

246
00:14:59,940 --> 00:15:00,774
<font color="japanese">エマ

247
00:15:04,904 --> 00:15:05,988
<font color="japanese">ウウウ…

248
00:15:06,071 --> 00:15:07,114
<font color="japanese">健夫

249
00:15:07,740 --> 00:15:09,199
<font color="japanese">もうやめよう

250
00:15:09,283 --> 00:15:10,910
<font color="japanese">苦しまなくていいの

251
00:15:11,911 --> 00:15:13,203
<font color="japanese">お願い

252
00:15:13,287 --> 00:15:14,997
<font color="japanese">もう苦しまないで！

253
00:15:15,497 --> 00:15:18,375
<font color="japanese">ウオオオオ…

254
00:15:21,462 --> 00:15:22,463
<font color="japanese">健夫

255
00:15:28,427 --> 00:15:30,971
<font color="japanese">形が… 変わった…

256
00:15:31,639 --> 00:15:34,725
<font color="japanese">なんて… 優しい輝きなの

257
00:15:52,576 --> 00:15:53,994
<font color="japanese">はっ…

258
00:16:05,673 --> 00:16:09,343
<font color="japanese">私に会いに
<font color="japanese">来てくれていたのか

259
00:16:10,469 --> 00:16:13,597
<font color="japanese">私に助けを求めていたのか

260
00:16:15,099 --> 00:16:16,058
<font color="japanese">なのに⸺

261
00:16:16,642 --> 00:16:19,603
<font color="japanese">私は何も気づかず…

262
00:16:29,238 --> 00:16:30,364
<font color="japanese">ああっ…

263
00:16:31,657 --> 00:16:34,201
<font color="japanese">おとう… さん…

264
00:16:42,001 --> 00:16:43,002
<font color="japanese">健夫

265
00:16:43,752 --> 00:16:45,337
<font color="japanese">すまなかった

266
00:17:01,353 --> 00:17:02,354
<font color="japanese">健夫…

267
00:17:05,816 --> 00:17:07,359
<font color="japanese">お母さん

268
00:17:17,036 --> 00:17:20,414
<font color="japanese">いつかは こうしなければ
<font color="japanese">ならないと思っていた

269
00:17:22,041 --> 00:17:23,542
<font color="japanese">健夫のためとはいえ⸺

270
00:17:24,043 --> 00:17:28,338
<font color="japanese">私は<font color="japanese">Ｕ-ＭＥＮ(ユーメン)<font color="japanese">と手を組み
<font color="japanese">ミュータント狩りに手を貸し

271
00:17:28,422 --> 00:17:31,133
<font color="japanese">多くの人々を
<font color="japanese">傷つけてしまった

272
00:17:33,302 --> 00:17:36,972
<font color="japanese">私の命で償いきれるものでは
<font color="japanese">ないけれど…

273
00:17:38,849 --> 00:17:41,226
<font color="japanese">ごめんなさい　チャールズ

274
00:17:42,311 --> 00:17:44,438
<font color="japanese">ダメーッ！

275
00:17:54,948 --> 00:17:56,200
<font color="japanese">健夫…

276
00:18:05,209 --> 00:18:06,710
<font color="japanese">ありがとう

277
00:18:09,296 --> 00:18:10,506
<font color="japanese">結衣(ゆい)

278
00:18:11,131 --> 00:18:14,218
<font color="japanese">これが健夫の意思だ

279
00:18:15,135 --> 00:18:16,220
<font color="japanese">たとえつらくとも⸺

280
00:18:17,679 --> 00:18:20,057
<font color="japanese">生きて 手を取り合う

281
00:18:20,933 --> 00:18:23,852
<font color="japanese">それが健夫の願いだ

282
00:18:28,440 --> 00:18:30,526
<font color="japanese">はっ… はっ…

283
00:18:31,068 --> 00:18:34,238
<font color="japanese">うっ… うううう…

284
00:18:35,447 --> 00:18:36,365
<font color="japanese">ううっ…

285
00:18:36,448 --> 00:18:37,699
<font color="japanese">あっ

286
00:18:42,788 --> 00:18:44,248
<font color="japanese">さよなら

287
00:18:45,082 --> 00:18:46,166
<font color="japanese">健夫

288
00:18:49,837 --> 00:18:50,963
<font color="japanese">生まれた時には

289
00:18:51,046 --> 00:18:53,507
<font color="japanese">ミュータントの
<font color="japanese">兆候はなかった

290
00:18:54,508 --> 00:18:56,844
<font color="japanese">幼い時
<font color="japanese">久子ちゃんたちの前で

291
00:18:56,927 --> 00:18:58,971
<font color="japanese">力を見せたのが始まりよ

292
00:19:00,139 --> 00:19:03,016
<font color="japanese">あなたが８年ほど前に
<font color="japanese">東北に来た時⸺

293
00:19:03,517 --> 00:19:05,269
<font color="japanese">健夫は覚醒したの

294
00:19:07,479 --> 00:19:10,107
<font color="japanese">私の息子に
<font color="japanese">生まれたばかりに⸺

295
00:19:10,858 --> 00:19:13,360
<font color="japanese">桁外れの能力を持ち

296
00:19:13,443 --> 00:19:17,531
<font color="japanese">しかも それを私が
<font color="japanese">覚醒させてしまったとは…

297
00:19:19,575 --> 00:19:21,994
<font color="japanese">これまで
<font color="japanese">多くのミュータントを

298
00:19:22,077 --> 00:19:25,038
<font color="japanese">自分の子供として
<font color="japanese">育ててきたというのに

299
00:19:25,873 --> 00:19:29,793
<font color="japanese">本当の息子を
<font color="japanese">自分自身の手で…

300
00:19:30,377 --> 00:19:31,295
<font color="japanese">でも⸺

301
00:19:31,879 --> 00:19:34,798
<font color="japanese">あの子は最後に笑ってくれた

302
00:19:35,674 --> 00:19:39,386
<font color="japanese">久子に
<font color="japanese">感謝しなければならないな

303
00:19:43,223 --> 00:19:43,807
<font color="japanese">あっ

304
00:19:46,393 --> 00:19:47,561
<font color="japanese">あたし…

305
00:19:49,438 --> 00:19:51,732
<font color="japanese">たとえ
<font color="japanese">つらい現実があっても

306
00:19:52,399 --> 00:19:54,860
<font color="japanese">私たちは
<font color="japanese">立ち上がらなければならない

307
00:19:56,445 --> 00:19:58,238
<font color="japanese">すべてのミュータントと

308
00:19:58,947 --> 00:20:00,866
<font color="japanese">人間の懸け橋となるために

309
00:20:02,951 --> 00:20:05,537
<font color="japanese">中には
<font color="japanese">死んだマスターマインドや

310
00:20:05,621 --> 00:20:06,496
<font color="japanese">拘束されている

311
00:20:06,580 --> 00:20:08,874
<font color="japanese">マグニートのような奴も
<font color="japanese">いるがな

312
00:20:08,957 --> 00:20:09,917
<font color="japanese">フンッ

313
00:20:10,584 --> 00:20:12,753
<font color="japanese">マグニートに
<font color="japanese">できることっつったら

314
00:20:12,836 --> 00:20:16,215
<font color="japanese">牢獄の中でチェス盤と
<font color="japanese">にらみ合うことぐらいさ

315
00:20:16,798 --> 00:20:21,094
<font color="japanese">愛や友情は 邪悪な力に
<font color="japanese">打ち勝つことができる

316
00:20:21,178 --> 00:20:21,887
<font color="japanese">あっ

317
00:20:22,471 --> 00:20:25,515
<font color="japanese">今回は君に
<font color="japanese">それを教えられたよ

318
00:20:26,099 --> 00:20:27,768
<font color="japanese">サイクロプス

319
00:20:28,268 --> 00:20:29,019
<font color="japanese">あ…

320
00:20:30,520 --> 00:20:31,813
<font color="japanese">これを君に

321
00:20:36,026 --> 00:20:37,444
<font color="japanese">これ…

322
00:20:37,527 --> 00:20:39,529
<font color="japanese">信頼し合える仲間

323
00:20:41,782 --> 00:20:43,408
<font color="japanese">その証しだ

324
00:20:43,492 --> 00:20:44,534
<font color="japanese">フッ

325
00:20:45,494 --> 00:20:46,954
<font color="japanese">ありがとう

326
00:20:47,496 --> 00:20:48,997
<font color="japanese">スコット！

327
00:20:49,081 --> 00:20:51,291
<font color="japanese">お… おい！

328
00:20:51,375 --> 00:20:55,087
<font color="japanese">でもね あたしはエマから
<font color="japanese">いろいろ教わったのよ

329
00:20:55,170 --> 00:20:55,712
<font color="japanese">あ…

330
00:20:55,796 --> 00:20:58,131
<font color="japanese">あなたも
<font color="japanese">エマから教わったらどう？

331
00:20:58,215 --> 00:20:58,882
<font color="japanese">ええ？

332
00:21:01,093 --> 00:21:02,052
<font color="japanese">フフッ

333
00:21:02,552 --> 00:21:05,639
<font color="japanese">あなたには教えることが
<font color="japanese">たくさんありそうね

334
00:21:06,139 --> 00:21:07,015
<font color="japanese">スコット

335
00:21:07,599 --> 00:21:08,976
<font color="japanese">んっ　フッ

336
00:21:09,726 --> 00:21:10,727
<font color="japanese">ところで

337
00:21:11,603 --> 00:21:15,023
<font color="japanese">帰るための乗り物が
<font color="japanese">黒コゲなんだけど？

338
00:21:15,649 --> 00:21:17,067
<font color="japanese">どうするよ

339
00:21:17,150 --> 00:21:18,026
<font color="japanese">あ～あ

340
00:21:30,038 --> 00:21:31,039
<font color="japanese">終わり

341
00:23:03,673 --> 00:23:06,426
<font color="japanese">“囚人 9288492
<font color="japanese">エリック･レーンシャー”

342
00:23:26,405 --> 00:23:30,992
<font color="japanese">Ｘ-ＭＥＮの戦いは続く…

